"enterprise_to_revenue":0.538,"shares_outstanding":12840000.0,"float_shares":2831429.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.75949997,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"fifty_two_week_high":112.95,"fifty_two_week_low":30.55,"fifty_day_average":49.6258,"two_hundred_day_avg":71.417,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":220.5,"all_time_low":35.0,"long_business_summary":"Storage Technologies and Automation Limited designs, manufactures, and installs metal storage racks, automated warehousing systems, shelving solutions, and structural storage facilities in India. The company offers racking solutions, including selective pallet, drive-in pallet, radio shuttle, cantilever, pallet flow, mobile pallet, and push back pallet racking; and shelving solutions comprising slotted angle, long span, bolts free, multi-tier, heavy duty, live, and supermarket shelving, as well as garment on hangers. It also provides automation solutions, such as conveyor systems, merge and sort, ASRS with crane and shuttle, vertical goods lift, radio shuttle, and pick/put to light; structural solutions, including mezzanine, stackable pallets, rack supported warehouses, pre-engineered buildings, and temperature-controlled warehouses; and consulting services comprising turnkey storage solutions, intralogistics design, warehouse management system, project commissioning, simulation, and rack inspections. Its products are used for commercial and industrial applications. It exports its products to the United Arab Emirates, Saudi Arabia, and Oman. The company serves oil and gas, automotive components and aerospace, food and beverages, pharmaceutical, textiles, retail, fast moving consumer goods, and e-commerce industries. Storage Technologies and Automation Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Bengaluru, India."}}